    "The studies ultimately selected for inclusion shared specific characteristics:",
    "They conducted empirical research on professional development (PD) projects related to STEM in China. 2.",
    "They investigated the impact of PD on the ability of teachers to integrate STEM subjects in Chinese classrooms.",
